Package Model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PriceChanger
    This is an empty interface Implemented by all classes that will be able to change the price of a ticket
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    Represents an Admin with access to the system An admin has editing rights (Update + Delete) to certain records
    Cinema
    Represents a Cinema A cinema has a type, seating plan and list of sessions in that cinema
    Cineplex
    Represents a Cineplex in the system A Cineplex has at least 3 cinemas
    Holiday
    Represents a Holiday for the system to referenced Mainly used to determine any markup in the price of ticket(s)
    Movie
    Represents a Movie
    Movie_Goer
    Represents an MovieGoer with access to the system An MovieGoer has very limited rights (mostly READ and CREATE)
    Review
    Represents a Review of a Movie in the system
    Seat
    Represents a Seat in the SeatingPlan
    SeatingPlan
    Represents a SeatingPlan SeatingPlan will be used to be assigned to Cinema Seats are labelled 1,2,3....x where x is the number of columns The first ID of seat at each row is 1, x+1, 2x+1...
    Session
    Represents a Session Each session will be assigned to a particular cinema by the cinema's code
    Transaction
    Represents a Transaction (or Booking)
    User
    Represents an User in the system
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description

    Enumerated type for better readability and easier referencing to attribute
    MovieType
    Enumerated type for better readability and easier referencing to attribute
    PriceType
    Enumerated type for better readability and easier referencing to attribute
